Candroid

GitHub

Candroid

seanpm2001/Candroid: Candroid is the ultimate Android BusyBox, and a complete open-source re-implementation of everything Android. Currently only available on Linux.

Apps

Candroid-App-Store

seanpm2001/Candroid-App-Store: Candroid does things different. The Candroid app store is a library of APK client wrappers (F-Droid, APKPure, etc.) For the main Candroid app store, try visiting the Candroid Market.

Candroid-Assistant

seanpm2001/Candroid-Assistant: Candroid Assistant is both a desktop guide and a voice assistant for the Candroid framework. It is designed to replace the Google Assistant found in Android, and also the desktop guide in early versions of Android (for example: Android 2.3)

Candroid-Battery-Monitor

seanpm2001/Candroid-Battery-Monitor: Candroid Battery Monitor is a battery health and usage monitor for Candroid.

Candroid-Calculator

seanpm2001/Candroid-Calculator: The Candroid calculator application, an alternative to the Google calculator found in Android

Candroid-Debug

seanpm2001/Candroid-Debug: Candroid Debug is a debugging tool for the Candroid framework/environment.

Candroid-Easter-Egg

seanpm2001/Candroid-Easter-Egg: Candroid Easter Egg is a set of hidden Easter Eggs for the Candroid framework/environment. It is designed to replace Android Easter Eggs, but not exactly the same way.

Candroid-FIleCabinet

seanpm2001/Candroid-FileCabinet: Candroid FileCabinet is a file manager app for the Candroid framework/environment. It is a replacement to the Google Files application.

Candroid-Keyboard

seanpm2001/Candroid-Keyboard: Candroid Keyboard is a keyboard application for the Candroid framework/environment, designed to replace both GBoard, and the default Android keyboard.

Candroid-Market

seanpm2001/Candroid-Market: Candroid Market is a replacement for the older Android Market for the Candroid framework/environment. It is designed differently than the Candroid App Store. The Candroid Market is a single distribution APK front.

Candroid-Mail

seanpm2001/Candroid-Mail: Candroid Mail is a email platform wrapper, which replaces GMail with ProtonMail, and other email sites. An alternative to the GMail app on Android.
seanpm2001/Candroid-Mail: Candroid Mail is a email platform wrapper, which replaces GMail with ProtonMail, and other email sites. An alternative to the GMail app on Android.

Candroid-Notepad

seanpm2001/Candroid-Notepad: Candroid Notepad is a notepad app for the Candroid framework/environment. It is not a replacement to an Android stock program, as Android never included a notepad

Candroid-Phone

seanpm2001/Candroid-Phone: Candroid Phone is a cellular phone call app for the Candroid framework/environment. It is a replacement to the Google Phone application.

Canroid-Photo-Viewer

seanpm2001/Candroid-Photo-Viewer: Candroid Photo Viewer is the default image viewer for Candroid. It supports all the image formats Android does, except it supports NetP instead of WebP.

Candroid-Tube

seanpm2001/Candroid-Tube: Candroid Tube is a video platform wrapper, which replaces YouTube with Vimeo, DailyMotion, BitTube, Reddit, and other video sites. An alternative to the YouTube app on Android.

Candroid-Catalog

seanpm2001/Candroid-Catalogue: The Candroid application catalog. Main repository: https://github.com/seanpm2001/Candroid/tree/main/Candroid-Catalogue

NetM

seanpm2001/NetM: NetM is a set of tools aimed at easing the conversion from and alternation from Googles WebM and WebP formats, and also view their content and metadata.

NetP

seanpm2001/NetP: An open source alternative to the WebP image format by Google.

NetV

seanpm2001/NetV: An open source alternative to the WebM video format by Google.
